{
  THIS IS THE KING OF THE JEWS
}

# Luke 23:39
Then one of the criminals who were hanged blasphemed Him, saying,
{
  If You are the Christ, save Yourself and us.
}

# Luke 23:40
But the other, answering, rebuked him, saying,
{
  Do you not even fear God,
  seeing you are under the same condemnation?

# Luke 23:41
  And we indeed justly,
  for we receive the due reward of our deeds;
