and said to them,
{
  Peace to you.
}

# Luke 24:37
But they were terrified and frightened,
and supposed they had seen a spirit.

# Luke 24:38
And He said to them,
{
  Why are you troubled?

  And why do doubts arise in your hearts?

# Luke 24:39
  Behold My hands and My feet,
